# Minimalist Photography Portfolio

This is a minimalist photography portfolio website built with React and Tailwind CSS. The design is inspired by the styles of Bryan Schutmaat and Matthew Genitempo, focusing on:
- Clean, serif typography
- Abundant whitespace
- Vertical flow gallery
- Minimal UI distractions

## Project Structure
- `index.html`: Main entry point with Tailwind configuration.
- `app.js`: Main application logic and routing state.
- `components/`: UI components (Header, Gallery, About, Contact).
- `data/`: Portfolio images data (currently using user-uploaded assets).

## Maintenance
- When adding new images, update `data/photos.js`.
- If new external resources are used, update `trickle/assets/`.
- Keep this README updated if the project structure changes significantly.